 Smart Dewatering Dashboard (IoT + AI + Solar)

This project is built for *Smart India Hackathon 2025*.  
It demonstrates a prototype of *Dewatering-as-a-Service (DaaS)* using:

 🌧 *Rainfall Prediction* → AI/ML Linear Regression
⚡ *Pump Scheduling* → Solar/Grid/Diesel decision
🔧 *Predictive Maintenance* → anomaly detection
💵 *Billing* → pay-per-liter model
🌍 *Carbon Credits* → CO₂ savings tracking
📡 *IoT Integration* → Protosy sensors via Firebase

🔹 How to Run Locally
bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
streamlit run app.py
